{"tid":2131975,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"有市民選擇公園午膳　認為社區中心人多與餐廳堂食無異","createTime":"2020-07-30T07:29:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T07:29:21.000Z","uid":241764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"da6c76075242a7f535905962227508b671b8d0e1","tid":2131975,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T07:29:21.000Z","msg":"在油麻地，仍有不少市民在社區中心對面的公園吃飯。市民陳先生表示，覺得社區中心人多，與餐廳堂食無分別，更不安全，反而公園空曠些。<br />\n<br />\n市民謝小姐表示，以為只有員工飯堂才有開放，完全不知道有社區中心開放，批評措施混亂，又質疑為何政府禁止堂食後，又開放社區中心讓人聚集吃飯，質疑「是否病毒不會進入社區中心」，對此感到疑惑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540786-20200730.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540786-20200730.htm&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhIV%2FGdaNkEJkjxlYCjQUfm8%3D&h=61ae5ff3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540786-20200730.htm&h=2f3e17f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540786-20200730.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}